OL,3,CDFDS confirm Easter routes following
OL,4,Cboat collision
OL,6,FDFDS Seaways will introduce another
OL,7,Fboat and expand its sailing schedule
OL,8,Fduring the Easter break for Jersey
OL,9,Fpassengers.
OL,11,FIt comes after the Tarifa Jet crashed
OL,12,Finto St Helier's Elizabeth Harbour on
OL,13,FSunday 29 March.
OL,15,FThe shipping operator will deploy
OL,16,Fanother vessel, Cote d'Albatre, to run
OL,17,Fa revised schedule between Portsmouth
OL,18,Fand Jersey.
OL,26,@xD@RswxD@[sp
