OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1775124136
OL,3,CDFDS confirm Easter routes following
OL,4,Cboat collision
OL,6,FSailings from Portsmouth will begin at
OL,7,F1pm on Friday (3 April) and will
OL,8,Fcontinue operating throughout the
OL,9,Fweekend.
OL,11,FMeanwhile, the Stena Vinga vessel will
OL,12,Frestart from Thursday evening (2
OL,13,FApril), running the route between
OL,14,FJersey and St Malo.
OL,16,FThe ferry company has also confirmed
OL,17,Fadditional departures on both Easter
OL,18,FSunday and Easter Monday.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/7
