FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1775124136
OL,3,CDFDS confirm Easter routes following
OL,4,Cboat collision
OL,6,FIn a statement, a DFDS spokesperson
OL,7,Fsaid: "DFDS has been working closely
OL,8,Fwith the ports of St Helier and St
OL,9,FMalo to maximise sailing availability.
OL,11,F"Customers affected by these schedule
OL,12,Fchanges will be contacted directly by
OL,13,Femail with their updated travel
OL,14,Farrangements."
OL,16,FMeanwhile, the Levante Jet - which is
OL,17,Fcurrently undergoing a planned refit
OL,18,Fin Dunkirk - is expected to return to
OL,19,Fservice next week to replace Tarifa
OL,20,FJet's services.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/7
