PN,38304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1775124136
OL,3,CDFDS confirm Easter routes following
OL,4,Cboat collision
OL,6,FThe Tarifa Jet, which can carry up to
OL,7,F769 passengers and 145 vehicles, had
OL,8,Fsailed from Saint-Malo and was docking
OL,9,Fin Jersey on Sunday evening (29 March)
OL,10,Fwhen it hit the port's east berth
OL,11,Floading ramp.
OL,13,FIt is now on its way to Portland near
OL,14,FWeymouth for repairs.
OL,16,FIn an update, a Ports of Jersey
OL,17,Fspokesperson said: "Tarifa Jet
OL,18,Fdeparted the harbour at 09:20 under
OL,19,Fher own power, supported by a Ports of
OL,20,FJersey pilot.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1775124136
OL,3,CDFDS confirm Easter routes following
OL,4,Cboat collision
OL,6,F"As a precaution, the St Malo tug
OL,7,FSolidor was connected on a forward
OL,8,Fsafety line, with the Ports of Jersey
OL,9,Ftug Devout escorting.
OL,11,F"Our inspections have identified some
OL,12,Flocalised damage to the East Berth.
OL,13,FOur in-house engineering team is
OL,14,Falready making good progress with
OL,15,Frepairs, and we expect the berth to be
OL,16,Ffully operational again in time for
OL,17,Fthe weekend.
OL,19,F"The West Berth remains unaffected and
OL,20,Ffully operational."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
