OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1775124136
OL,3,CDFDS confirm Easter routes following
OL,4,Cboat collision
OL,6,FDespite the change to routes to help
OL,7,Fbolster passenger services, DFDS has
OL,8,Fwarned some businesses in Jersey that
OL,9,Fthere is disruption to the transport
OL,10,Fof freight later this month.
OL,12,FThe Stena Vinga will be going into dry
OL,13,Fdock between Wednesday 15 April and
OL,14,FSaturday 25 April.
OL,16,FThe borrowed Cote d'Albatre will take
OL,17,Fover the Stena Vinga route, but
OL,18,Fcarries less freight, so companies
OL,19,Fhave been warned to bring their
OL,20,Fshipments forward.
OL,26,@xD@OswxD@Xsp
